Processing of blood samples: 4-5ml of the blood sample will be centrifuged to isolate serum;
S100B, IL-1b, IL-6, NSE levels will be investigated at D0 (T0+6h, T0+12h where T0 is seizure
time) D14-D28. The remaining blood and cells will be stored at -80°C for future analyses.
